test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (4 == 3)
 +  where 4 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x79872533ac00>([-97])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x79872533ac00> = [[1, -97], [1, -97, 1], [-97], [-97, 1], [1, -97], [1, -97, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 97 == -97
 +  where 97 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -97])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
